01:05:25.343 --> 01:05:27.845
Jebo te pas!
Odakle on ovdje?

01:05:28.012 --> 01:05:30.431
Jer u Hard Newsu

01:05:31.265 --> 01:05:32.433
vjerujemo...

01:05:33.851 --> 01:05:36.354
Vjerujemo da smo spremni

01:05:36.479 --> 01:05:38.022
i na prvoj crti.

