01:22:02.631 --> 01:22:04.133
Baš je jebeno fenomenalan.

01:22:04.258 --> 01:22:07.470
Bogatiji je od Boga
i ima lutku vrlo lijepe veličine.

01:22:07.637 --> 01:22:08.804
Tako je.

01:22:09.430 --> 01:22:12.141
I odgovaramo si vrlo lijepo na papiru.

01:22:13.309 --> 01:22:14.602
Kako se to zna?

01:22:15.144 --> 01:22:16.479
Samo treba imati vjere.

01:22:16.646 --> 01:22:18.230
