samo zato što ti je ona kao dom.

01:25:27.837 --> 01:25:29.630
Moram pronaći Marka.

01:25:36.345 --> 01:25:37.638
Halo, Pierce.

01:25:38.347 --> 01:25:39.348
Bridget je.

01:25:39.515 --> 01:25:41.017
Trebao bi mi Mark.

01:25:41.142 --> 01:25:44.353
