dok si ti uz njega.

01:29:03.511 --> 01:29:04.512
Dođi.

01:29:04.637 --> 01:29:06.138
Treba se posvetiti kampanji.

01:29:06.472 --> 01:29:07.723
Mjesta, mjesta.

01:29:07.848 --> 01:29:10.059
Prolazi samohrana trudnica.

01:29:12.019 --> 01:29:13.521
Laura, Josh.

01:29:14.230 --> 01:29:17.525
Moramo dati šest minuta
generalu Luu Tongu, okej?

01:29:17.984 --> 01:29:19.735
